  borderObjectName: CAMPUCHIA
  countryDescription: "\u0110\u01B0\u1EDDng bi\xEAn gi\u1EDBi \u0111\u1EA5t li\u1EC1n
    Vi\u1EC7t Nam - Campuchia d\xE0i kho\u1EA3ng 1.270 km, b\u1EAFt \u0111\u1EA7u
    t\u1EEB ng\xE3 ba bi\xEAn gi\u1EDBi Vi\u1EC7t - L\xE0o - Campuchia (Qu\u1EA3ng
    Ng\xE3i) v\xE0 k\u1EBFt th\xFAc t\u1EA1i \u0111i\u1EC3m gi\xE1p bi\u1EC3n v\u1ECBnh
    Th\xE1i Lan (An Giang).\n\n\u0110\u01B0\u1EDDng bi\xEAn gi\u1EDBi n\xE0y \u0111i
    qua 8 t\u1EC9nh: Qu\u1EA3ng Ng\xE3i, Gia Lai, \u0110\u1EAFk L\u1EAFk, L\xE2m
    \u0110\u1ED3ng, \u0110\u1ED3ng Nai , T\xE2y Ninh, \u0110\u1ED3ng Th\xE1p v\xE0
    An Giang. \u0110\u1ECBa h\xECnh khu v\u1EF1c bi\xEAn gi\u1EDBi chuy\u1EC3n ti\u1EBFp
    t\u1EEB v\xF9ng \u0111\u1ED3i n\xFAi cao nguy\xEAn \u1EDF ph\xEDa B\u1EAFc xu\u1ED1ng
    v\xF9ng \u0111\u1ED3ng b\u1EB1ng s\xF4ng C\u1EEDu Long b\u1EB1ng ph\u1EB3ng,
    v\u1EDBi h\u1EC7 th\u1ED1ng s\xF4ng ng\xF2i v\xE0 k\xEAnh r\u1EA1ch ch\u1EB1ng
    ch\u1ECBt, t\u1EA1o \u0111i\u1EC1u ki\u1EC7n thu\u1EADn l\u1EE3i cho vi\u1EC7c
    ph\xE1t tri\u1EC3n kinh t\u1EBF c\u1EEDa kh\u1EA9u v\xE0 giao l\u01B0u v\u0103n
    h\xF3a gi\u1EEFa nh\xE2n d\xE2n v\xF9ng bi\xEAn."
